            "'The Calling of Saint Matthew' is part of a trio of paintings depicting the life of Saint Matthew, all commissioned for the Contarelli Chapel.",
            "Caravaggio’s revolutionary use of light and shadow in this painting greatly influenced the Baroque movement and subsequent generations of artists.",
